title: Jacquees Interview and More

description:
12/6/18 - Today on the show we had Jacquees stop by where he spoke about his album, bonding with Birdman, Ella Mai Remix Removal and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Lil pump for missing out on a bag and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
